          "description": "I\u2019ve been coming here for the last couple of months, it depends what doctor/ provider takes your case that you are going to receive a good treatment.\nMy biggest complain here is that if you want to book or reschedule an appointment you have to come straight up to the hospital, because every time I call they pick up and leave me on hold for the longest time and then just hung up, I was in so much pain trying to re schedule an appointment and that\u2019s exactly what happened, I had to come to the hospital as an emergency for them to schedule me, I had to wait 2 hrs for an emergency walk in visit, cause in google says 9am walk ins I got there at 8:30 and they told me they start at 10 am, then again that\u2019s why I tried to speak to someone on the phone I also spoke to the receptionist to change the provider and they told me I had to wait for someone to call during the week or next week, so now I gotta wait for a call to continue my treatment plan with someone else\u2026 if you are lucky you get a good provider from the beginning\u2026 just make your appointments at the hospital\u2026 they aren\u2019t that professional",
